## To remove a header from your snapshot

Create a transform:

Select the traffic you want to be affected by the transform  
![][image1]

Next select in the next column the source.  I deselect and then choose HTTP Header  
![][image2]

I then put in the name of the field you want to remove and select 0 for the index then click save  
![][image3]

In the next column I select type and choose constant  
![][image4]

Next I leave the field empty and click save  
![][image5]

Make sure you press save again otherwise you will lose your changes  
![][image6]

Now you have removed the field from the header at replay.    
![][image7]

To check it you can click on the repair that has a yellow indicator and scroll down the header column and you can now see the data has been removed
